.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE_ALIAS_LOOKUP" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-alias-lookup \- look up alias for a node ID
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-alias-lookup
.I <arg>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns alias and color for the given node ID from the gossip graph.
.PP
Output: JSON object or array from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
